  "texts": [
    "We utilized the platform to compute and download the co-occurring results for seven ethnic groups across 1500 years.",
    "For each case, we selected the top 300 words, excluding the names of the ethnic groups.",
    "Each word underwent scoring using a sentiment classification model for classical Chinese 12, which outputs probabilities for five sentiment degrees ranging from extremely negative to extremely positive.",
    "Finally, for each case, the sentiment scores were summed with word frequency weighting.",
    "We examined the average probability of extremely negative sentiment in co-occurring vocabulary, as displayed in Fig. 9d."
  ],
